In the Americas region, revenue was up in all four industrial businesses led by Smart Infrastructure with double-digit growth. Within the region in the U.S., Mobility and Siemens Healthineers reported slight revenue decreases.

In the Asia, Australia region, revenue was up by on double-digit increase at Mobility, followed by revenue growth at Digital Industries and Smart Infrastructure. As with orders, revenue development both in the region and in China was held back by strong negative currency

